trans-unit.source: Error handler for publishing SOAP-enabled services in COM+ applications.
trans-unit.target: Feil behandlingsprogram for publiseringstjenester SOAP-aktivert i COM +-programmer.

trans-unit.source: The ComSoapPublishError class provides a static <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ComSoapPublishError.Report%2A> method for writing to an event log errors that were encountered while publishing SOAP-enabled COM interfaces in COM+ applications.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ComSoapPublishError gir statiske <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ComSoapPublishError.Report%2A>metode for å skrive til en feil som oppstod under publisering av SOAP-aktiverte COM-grensesnitt i COM +-programmer.</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ComSoapPublishError.Report%2A>

trans-unit.source: ComSoapPublishError is used internally by the .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: ComSoapPublishError er brukt internt av .NET Framework.

trans-unit.source: You do not need to use the class directly in your code.
trans-unit.target: Du trenger ikke å bruke klassen direkte i koden.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ComSoapPublishError"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ComSoapPublishError"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Writes to an event log an error encountered while publishing SOAP-enabled COM interfaces in COM+ applications.
trans-unit.target: Skriver en hendelseslogg den oppstod en feilen under publisering av SOAP-aktiverte COM-grensesnitt i COM +-programmer.

trans-unit.source: The Report method is used internally by the .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: Metoden rapporten er brukt internt av .NET Framework.
